%% TrustyAI Explainability - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant MM as ModelMesh Serving
    participant KS as KServe<br/>(Inference Logger)
    participant Consumer as TrustyAI Consumer<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant CloudEvt as CloudEvent Consumer<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant MMRecon as ModelMesh Payload<br/>Reconciler
    participant KSRecon as KServe Payload<br/>Reconciler
    participant Store as DataSource<br/>(PVC/MinIO/Memory)
    participant Scheduler as PrometheusScheduler<br/>(@Scheduled)
    participant Core as explainability-core<br/>(SPD, DIR, Drift)
    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>(/q/metrics)
    participant User as User / Dashboard
    participant Explainer as Explainer Endpoint<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant GRPCClient as KServe v2 gRPC Client
    participant Model as Model Server<br/>gRPC

    Note over MM, Store: Flow 1: ModelMesh Inference Payload Ingestion
    MM->>Consumer: POST /consumer/kserve/v2<br/>HTTP 80/TCP, No Auth
    Consumer->>MMRecon: Forward payload (in-process)
    MMRecon->>MMRecon: Reconcile partial input/output<br/>into complete prediction
    MMRecon->>Store: Store prediction record<br/>File I/O or HTTP 9000/TCP

    Note over KS, Store: Flow 2: KServe CloudEvent Inference Ingestion
    KS->>CloudEvt: CloudEvent POST<br/>HTTP 80/TCP, No Auth
    Note right of CloudEvt: org.kubeflow.serving.<br/>inference.request/response
    CloudEvt->>KSRecon: Forward payload (in-process)
    KSRecon->>KSRecon: Reconcile request/response<br/>events into prediction
    KSRecon->>Store: Store prediction record<br/>File I/O or HTTP 9000/TCP

    Note over Scheduler, Prom: Flow 3: Fairness Metric Calculation (Scheduled)
    Scheduler->>Store: Read prediction data (in-process)
    Store-->>Scheduler: Prediction records
    Scheduler->>Core: Calculate SPD/DIR metrics
    Core-->>Scheduler: Metric values
    Scheduler->>Scheduler: Publish to Micrometer gauge<br/>(trustyai_spd, trustyai_dir)
    Prom->>Consumer: GET /q/metrics<br/>HTTP 80/TCP<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    Consumer-->>Prom: Prometheus metrics response

    Note over User, Model: Flow 4: Model Explanation Request
    User->>Explainer: POST /explainers/local/lime<br/>HTTP 80/TCP, No Auth
    Explainer->>GRPCClient: Prepare inference request
    GRPCClient->>Model: gRPC ModelInfer<br/>plaintext, No Auth
    Model-->>GRPCClient: Inference response
    GRPCClient-->>Explainer: Prediction result
    Explainer->>Core: Run LIME/SHAP/CF algorithm
    Core-->>Explainer: Explanation result
    Explainer-->>User: JSON explanation response<br/>HTTP 80/TCP
